To make a cake, you'll need ingredients like flour, sugar, eggs, and butter. You can find many cake recipes online or in cookbooks. Would you like a specific recipe or some general tips on cake-making?
tell me recipe of cake step by step

Here's a simple recipe for a classic cake: Ingredients: 2 cups all-purpose flour, 1 teaspoon baking powder, 1 teaspoon salt, 1 cup unsalted butter, softened, 1 3/4 cups granulated sugar, 3 large eggs, 2 teaspoons vanilla extract. Instructions: Preheat oven to 350째F (180째C). Grease two 9-inch (23cm) round cake pans. Whisk together flour, baking powder, and salt. Beat butter and sugar until light and fluffy. Beat in eggs one at a time, then beat in vanilla extract. With mixer on low speed, gradually add flour mixture to wet ingredients and mix until just combined. Divide batter evenly between prepared pans. Bake 30-35 minutes or until toothpick inserted in center comes out clean. Let cool in pans 10 minutes before transferring to wire rack to cool completely.
